FBIS3-39420 "drweu032_l_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-032 Document Type:Daily Report 16 Feb 1994 SPAIN Solana Says Russia's Role in Bosnia `Essential' LD1502221994 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network in Spanish 1900 GMT 15 Feb 94 LD1502221994 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] Spanish Foreign Minister Javier Solana said today that Russia has a role to play in the Bosnian peace process. [Begin Solana recording] No one wants to leave Russia out of the solution to the Yugoslav problem. It must play a part, it has to play a part, its role is essential, and this is the view of all the European Union countries and all the Atlantic alliance countries. [end recording]
